{"tid":1593110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望唔好圍差館但又要留到最後一刻","createTime":"2019-09-25T02:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T12:54:50.000Z","uid":156878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f812496e2f6b09c671b5c7cfa97f0676f43051a0","tid":1593110,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:27:46.000Z","msg":"好多時人地報哂陣，好容易會捉到十個八個。<br />\n<br />\n唔好見到防暴跑自己先跑。同一戰術用太多佢地就會變陣。而且走唔切被捕既代價太大。<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要諗新既抗爭方式。"},{"pid":"33f0bc89e97df4c28dfb046af5a97a7a294ae9ea","tid":1593110,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"ce2588a08d585f3eebbd49af637ccf4f5ec3375d","tid":1593110,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"都唔知圍嚟做乜鳩 肥羊送上門 去自首呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n左膠即使戴晒gear都依然係一個左膠 仍然樂於送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n與其圍差館鳩嗌鳩企 不如玩返以前嗰套 靜坐舉手絕食算啦 起碼慳返唔少gear錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7184e8d889a9bcde8e7535c9a2f78ec8587d144f","tid":1593110,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}